{"tid":2316604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌警告：倘葵盛西邨同邨多座有確診 或須全區封鎖","createTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T04:37:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d494eabb711edad4f25d8b36be81609d59e09c24","tid":2316604,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"葵盛西邨第8座爆發武漢肺炎，當局昨安排5樓居民接受強制檢測，但有大廈居民漏夜搬離，惹播毒風險。政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌今早在港台節目表示，當局應盡早安排葵盛西邨第8座5樓接受強制檢測，建議5樓居民在等候結果前要盡量留在家，不要到親友家中，以免傳播病毒。他又說，若同座有不同樓層再現新個案，有需要考慮安排整棟樓的住戶強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌說，如果葵盛西邨第8座有三個樓層都有確診個案，便要考慮全座大廈居民都要做強制檢測，因為可能病毒經過共用地方傳播。他指葵盛西邨居民接受檢測的反應良好，若此情況下暫毋須整幢居民強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，現時社區源頭不明的個案仍然多，葵盛西邨第1座有確診個案，亦未與5座的個案彼此相關，但若發現同一屋邨有多座都有確診，就要小心留意，有機會要全區封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d0653c805637de1b27396d15cba72bf6afe2ac","tid":2316604,"uid":275498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搬走"},{"pid":"330f9d255ad32131aedc7a0b017731bf85a0bb0f","tid":2316604,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國式防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防疫要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7269954feb823d79be62063620844a2ebe9d3b3b","tid":2316604,"uid":275498,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">但有大廈居民漏夜搬離</span></strong>"},{"pid":"414abf35d4dfb9fb9be5cbf0faa676fd98c2c104","tid":2316604,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"全區封係咪想入去返工都唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b2997c5cd55592636f64f387199ace290d50a6","tid":2316604,"uid":4527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"全境封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda6f67887f494f097baa403aa1e2a97a7b75a79","tid":2316604,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c47877f1f2c6eb0e3be3fe03ea1bc9e029dbe43","tid":2316604,"uid":140737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"不用PS4,也能玩全境封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4bb98abb25528f874fd0a003c52ea7bc1cc698","tid":2316604,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"叫佢地快走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c37452f2e461f03b7447511a6bef7b8c201851","tid":2316604,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"走人啦 走人啦"},{"pid":"cf6f54da4d8d2053290ff9e760309b1ab0925c8c","tid":2316604,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:30:32.000Z","msg":"屌, 上次SARS就淘大 38萬<br />\n今次反而係公屋  無得38萬買私樓了"},{"pid":"7be4b4390c007f16d5e7009aa93ce8b8b8994d8c","tid":2316604,"uid":8762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf6f54da4d8d2053290ff9e760309b1ab0925c8c","tid":2316604,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:30:32.000Z","msg":"屌, 上次SARS就淘大 38萬<br />\n今次反而係公屋  無得38萬買私樓了